text:
Super friendly staff who are happy to assist with your orders, burgers are not bad (well cooked!l and the chips are great. Serving sizes are a good size.
Service is quite fast (note that I came at around 11.45am)
One of my favorite places to grab burgers and fries. Sometimes the seasoning or the portion of fries are off but that's ok. Still love the food.
Can't go wrong with their fries and burger. Staff firendly and really fast.
Simply the best burger chain there is, the famous fries are hard to beat!
Excelent! Great! The best burguer I have tested.  Prices good. Startimg 9usd. Free topings. Juicy meat... great chese... recomended 100%
Great customer service , Food hot & delicious, atmosphere of store was outgoing and happy.
Great (fast food burger) compared to the usual suspects as McDonald's and Burger King. Atmosphere is quite relaxed with some good places to eat your burger on bar style tables. Would come here again!
Best customer service I've had in NYC, while cleaning , and throwing out my garbage, the five guys employee helped me and calmed down the customers that were rushing us.

I thought my own expectations of this place would make me disappointed.... But I made the lovely discovery that it didn't. Great burger, amazing fries and superb staff. My only disappointment is that they are not avaliable in Sweden....yet

Nice place when your tired and need some jazz
Away from the street.

The sandwiches are ready just before you finish paying (so it's reeeeeally a fast-food restaurant), and they're delicious. I didn't have a problem with finding a seat, but if you go during the weekend or lunch time, you can have a problem with that.

very delicious burger and fries.
one of the best burgers I've ever tasted.
Its worth the price!
Always a great burger at 5-guys
Cheeseburger, little fries and small drink $21.09. Burger was delicious. Fries had way too much salt on them. Someone has a heavy hand. All in all pretty good.
Very tasty and clean place with excellent service.
Super friendly staff. Great burger goes without saying. Awsome Coke Zero dispenser with freaking lemon zero

I've heard lots about Five Guys burgers and just had to try it for myself. On a recent trip to New York City, I saw an outlet and tried their burger and fries. I was not disappointed! They tasted great! Looking forward to my next trip!
Very nice fast food with the best hamburger in new york. The service was very good with many friendly people

Food-wise, it's good honest food. Love the fries made from Idaho spuds. More flavorful than those in other chains. Love the idea of their serving free peanuts. I appreciate this gesture of hospitality. Would love to see a cleaner toilet.

The burgers here are delicious! Fresh made to order, you can't go wrong. Not to mention you choose your own toppings! The fries, like the burgers are fresh made to order as well. Sometimes it can get crowded and seating is limited, BUT if you want fresh food, this is your place!!

Convenient location in the area. It gets too crowded on weekends and especially around Christmas, since it's one of the few places that let you use the restroom. This location is not as big as others, so you won't find seats available all the time. Overall great place to have one of the best burgers in the city.

A great burger served quickly every time. The fries are amazing. The Coke Freestyle is a blessing (diet caffeine free vanilla Coke thank-you-very-much). This location, while a little small, is fine. Don't count on eating in the store but you're not far from somewhere to sit and eat.
Best "junk food" spots in the city. You just can't stop eating the fries...
Good food and very friendly service.

Food, tasty as always, super fast.

Only thing I didn't love: no shakes at that location.

Got delivery from Five Guys the other day! Everything was fresh and still hot despite the fact that we waited 30minutes for delivery!The burger was nice and juicy, the fries were also really hot and delicious! The price is pretty standart for nice burger in Manhattan!
My favorite burgers, I simply love them. They are not expensive. You can build your burger choosing from the toppings list. Do not leave without trying the cajun fries
Usually give 5 stars to all five guys. The issue with the fries being over fried isnt the fault of the staff there were only 3 people working on a Sunday in a very busy tourist area.
Great veggie sandwich! Was surprised to even find one lol
Place was busy during my visit. Service at the counter was great but you had to clean your own table. Food tasted good as usual.

For me One of the best burgers of NYC. The meat was juicy, cheese was tasty... I took an all the way cheeseburger and it was delicious. Also the burger was packed correctly and it was still hot when I came back at the hotel.
Great burgers and fries.  Used the Five Guys app and had my food very quickly after I walked in the door.  This location doesn't have many tables, so it may be hard to find a seat.
Everything is fresh including beef and made to order. A little pricey but much better than any other fast food burgers. They have also good milkshake and french fries
Great food ... Burgers made to order. Fries are delicious and plentiful ... Love the Cajun seasoning! I'm not a peanut lover, but my friends enjoyed the peanuts while waiting for the burgers.
I really like this place. I hope to eat Five Guys in Korea.
Solid well made healthy burger without the fuss. Be sure to get a side a cajun fries and don't go beyond the little size, since Five Guys prides itself on it's generous portions.
As always, as expected, cheese burger and cheese hotdogs, never lets you down

The food was delicious. But personally, I wouldn't like eating in there since It gets hot and stuffy because of the kitchen which isn't really a problem. But If you don't like being in a very warm place, you should take your food and eat outside. The employees were nice and there are no real problems with this location
Burger and fries are really good. But there are some improvements on the service. For example please more restrooms are required definitely.
Fresh food & fast service for being in New York.

Very good burger and fries. Choose your base (cheeseburger, hamburger) and if you want a little or normal size (2 steaks for the latter) and add any toppings you want for free. Quick service too and no issues with my order.

Delicious burgers and fries. No free peanuts,  like other FG locations.  Most likely the most food your money can buy in the city,  specially after considering that just 2 restaurants away a cup of coffee starts at $12.50

Their burgers and fries are 100% awesome. Gotta stop by there for lunch 1 day

Rating: 100/100
Best burger and fries always made to perfection hands down.
Always a great burger and amazing fries. Limited sit down room

A nice place to have a fresh cheeseburger and some fries. It was my frist time at Five Guys. I like the simplicity, but still the wide selection. The restaurant is located right next to the Rockefeller center.

This Five Guys can get crowded at times during lunch, but usually the wait is not too bad. Like every Five Guys location, they fill the bag up with fries, so always order a small fry; it will be plenty.

I went here because I figured it would be less crowded than the one in Times Square.  I was right.  Food was as good as at the other places and no lines.  Plenty of empty seats.  There's steps coming down at the entrance though.  I think it would be better if the steps had a handrail and also a ramp for wheelchairs.
Best cheap burger I ever had.

This particular Five Guys was nice, though the lines felt a little cluttered and confusing.  Other than that, the food is the same quality as you'd get from any other and there are still free peanuts!
Burgers are delicious, hot and freshly made while you wait. The fries were salty buy equally has delicious.

The cashier here was very nice to me the last time I was here and the burger I ordered here was delicious. As always you have to get the Cajun fries. Only negative is the seating space here is very small.
Once you get past the sticker shock of an $11 hamburger the food is really good.  The staff was also friendly and fast considering how busy they were.
Very good burgers!
Really good fries, kind of dirty/sticky but I would come back for the fries
The best burger I ate in America. Just amazing. Try for your self, you will not regret. Furthermore it is a very good price.
Always great there,, never a disappointment
I always go to Five Guys for fresh fries. They are the best fries and value for the money. Staff was friendly.
Always perfect. The best hamburgers in the universe.

Pretty nice place. Walk in, grab your own plate that closes, choose from a wide variety of hot food, pay, walk upstairs that has tables with chairs and one TV. Bathroom available to wash hands. The prices are reasonable. I was satisfied.
The food and the staff is great here. I wish 5Guys had a tip bowl around. So we can tip the staff after great fresh made burger.
Really great burgers and frech fries. Very friendly staff but interior is a bit small with limited amount of seats. All that for a good price.
Extremely busy during lunch hours with inadequate seating arrangement. Vegetarian options are limited. However, food is good and they provide with free peanuts to kill your waiting time. :)
Awesome burgers! The 5 Guys burger never never lacks in consistancy, although the fries may sometimes be under/overcooked they're generous in serving.
Fast and friendly. Tasty too. Always be careful if you have a nut allergy as they cook their fries in peanut oil.
Definitely a good burger and good customization options. The fries aren't the best bang for your buck, but the free peanuts definitely make up for it.
Best Burger and fries... take it all the way!

The East Coast's Answer to In N' Out, these awesome-ly yummy burgers are a calorie-buster, but a satisfying one at that.  The plethora of sauces and options only sweeten the treat, as are the free peanuts available.
Great tasting burgers and food. I gave it 4 stars because of the cost and sometimes they just toss my fries in the bag. No big deal though.
Great burgers, moderately priced, nice decor but slow service.  Still a good place to try if you are in the mood for fast-food-style burgers.
Great burgers and fries! Everything tasted super fresh and delicious; delivers what they promise =)
Hands down the best Burgers, Fries and great prices.
Very friendly staff.  Great food.  Very generous portion of fries.
Ordered a cheese burger with everything and Cajun fries, portion was huge, flavor was on the spot. Oh, don't forget to try their free peanuts.
Great burgers. Service was great. They actually came out and cleaned the tables because they saw it was dirty. Not expecting that in a burger joint in NYC.
A nice, normally-priced a fast food burger place. I had Cheeseburger with 3-4 topping moreover, you get free unlimited toppings and, you can get fries on the side. lol
A good place to grab a quick bite! Quite full because of the location - nonetheless delicious like every other five guys. Reasonable prices here.
Awesome burgers and fries and the best part, still very reasonably priced. Staff is always very upbeat and friendly.
You can't go wrong if you're a meat eater if you're not this place will change your mind for sure... best burgers best fries
Nice and clean location. Food is great! The fries... OMG. Friendly staff. Fast service. What more can you ask for?
Great burger and fries !!! Meaty and juicy :) many options of sodas to choose from ! But the food are little slow tho, the staffs are super friendly :)
I really enjoyed the burger and fries i had. Was really good. Service was friendly.
Pretty busy on a weekend, but good food and great portions.
It's a standard five guys, big burgers and heaps of fires for a reasonable price. Ate here before tree lighting This year, it gave me the strength to deal with the a-holes on line.
Recommend getting a double cheeseburger with bacon. Watched a documentary on this chain, it's actually seems like healthier option than some of the alternatives when you look at their ingredients.
They have a great burger, for a fast food/quick order type place.
The crew here is awesome. I frequent this location and many of them know me by face. They are friendly and the food is always great.
Best burgers, that's it.
Good 5 Guys. As it should be. Good burgers, fries, and staff. Recommended... Nothing to see here except an awesome 5 Guys experience.
Reallu good burger and fries. Fantastic drink selection. Not a fancy place but good food.
Good sandwich just messed up the order. Make sure you check you food before you leave.
They're always nice, the burgers are always on point and exactly how I ordered it. Great job.
Testy burgers and fries to die for..loved it
It's a nice burger, a wide selection of drinks but you can have a better burger for less price
I love their Burgers. This store is a busy store still fast.
Great burgers from a great chain. Fries are good too. Just be prepared to eat a lot of fries.
Nice staff they had patience with me. I appreciate them working during this pandemic. The food was great!
Everyone one loves their Burgers but they have the best Fries specially the Cajun Fries.
Clean, good service and the food was nice as always at Five Guys.
Best burgers worldwide!
always love to stop by at this place when in manhattan.
Nice burgers and fries, best to eat it inside so the fries won't get soggy.
Very good, I like the boorger
Great Five Guys. Crowded and a little messy. French fries according to my friends where not as good as at other 5 guys.
Good burguers and fries, small place. Came in with my son after visiting the Nintendo shop across the street.
Lovely little Five Guys with great service and friendly customers.
Love their burgers, been to many across the country and they are consistently good
Delicious hamburger's it's enough order the regular fries, order the hamburger with all ingredients
One of the best burgers in town, just wish they would clean the floor from time to time
One of the best burgers on the go. No line. Get drinks elsewhere.
Food is excellent! Great service. Can be a little crowded during lunch time.
Great fast service..and our food was soooo fresh. Cudos to this great team.
Great tasting burgers and the fries cooked in peanut oil and pretty good too.
Favorite burger place, but this particular location has minimal seating given the space if you're hoping to eat in
Good food customer service kinda shady but a great experience never the less.
Nice juicy burgers, great fries, plenty of options to choose from. Nice and friendly staff.
Good burger better fries kinda expensive but it's NYC kinda of expected
Five guys is five guys, consistent
The best fast food chain in the USA, regarding burgers at least. Just awesome.
One of the best burgers you'll ever have and great fries.
Really love the juicy burger!
So tasty burger, fast service, friendly staff it's just the best in town
Amazing!!!! Service was great & food was even better. Wish they would put paper towels in the bathroom though. Lol
Excellent burgers, spectacular fries. Not for anyone with peanut allergies.
Always the best burger in the area! Great service as well
Nice little place to grab a good burger at a good price, especially considering it's location.
It's good. The kind of burger that you regret eating only couple of hours later.
Good burgers, good french fries, great price = good place to eat.
The place was super clean late at night. Clean Restrooms, too.  Staff was nice in service.
Burgers are delicious, fresh and tasty. Love their fries.
Good for a quick meal, bit oily though. Service was fast.
Very tasty and fresh fast food. The staff was very professional. A must try place.
It's 5 guys. You know what to expect if you've been here before. Service was a bit slow and appeared understaffed but they were still nice
Great food.  A bit lengthy of a wait and a crowded and somewhat unorganized pick up process
Service was fast, food was really good. Can't complain about that.
Great hamburgers but on the expensive side. Good quality and you get peanuts for free.
5 guys are awesome pretty much wherever you go. Both service and food were great at this location!
As usual good burgers and even better fries. comfortable

Great burger, nice service.
Only one restroom a bit of an issue though.
Good food. Fast. Good and quick. Great service. Nice service. Would recommend.
Good burger adapted to the price. A bit heavy, but the products are fresh
Have it your way.  One order of fries is enough for two.  We really enjoy it here.
Good old five guys, cam be busy but they serve quickly! Nice amount of seating to.
Awesome hamburgers! They are little bit expensive but they do their job really good.
Not bad place to eat a good burger before the Radio city Hall show
Love 5 guys burgers a lil pricey but we'll worth it
Four stars, they deserve - if they hadn't forgotten the meat in the burger!  They gave me a new burger
Very busy, but fast service! Food is delicious along with friendly staff.
A bit pricey for what they suggest. The fries are really good.
Small and pretty crowded but nice staff and the best fast food burgers you can get
Always love their burgers, fries and fountain drinks.
Good Five Guys...  Awesome burger and fries...  Lots of seating, good service...
Solid burgers and great fries. Always go for the cajun fries.
Excellent 5Gs burgers at this location. Great staff
T H E Best hamburger in the US
Always happy at this place... great burgers and great fries
Tasty burger. Location is a bit of a hole though. Friendly staff.
Five Guys in NYC, great burgers near Rockerfeller Center I will be bcak next time I am in town.
Can get busy, but it's worth it.  Great food and quick service
Haven't been here in years. Loved the hot dog!
Great taste, great service. I popped in for a quick bite to eat on way to Broadway.
The burgers are delicious
The best burguer! However the infrastructure is not that clean
Love the burgers and the fries here. They are amazing.
Delicious burgers and fries, excellent customer service
Awesome burguer and fries best ones I eat at NYC
Outstanding burgers! Would definitely return and munch some more :)
Great food and fast service!
Simply the best place to have a burger with fries.
My favorite burger meal in the city - double bacon cheeseburger with small fries and a handful of peanuts!
Delicious burgers and fries. Very friendly staff.
Tables could be a little battery customized and cleaner
Great burgers and affordable prices near 5th av
Certified yummy burguer
excellent
It has a limited type of burgers but they are the best.
Nice flavor, not the nest but is good.
Good burgers and fries than the more overrated burger restaurant options
Nice food, the free peanuts are a good detail
Good food. Quick service. Not very clean
Great burgers, and free peanuts. Just awesome
Very fast service, seating fairly spaced
Silas Nacita was right -  very tasty burgers!!! Also friendly staff
Lots of options for add ons and sizes. Get the minis if you don't have a big appetite.
GREAT CUSTER SERVICE AND FAST SERVICE TOO. BEST FIVE GUYS I EVER WENT TO.
Burgers were good, fries was tasty
Love the burgers esp. the Little Cheeseburger, All the Way!
Perfect fast food. Love the fries especially!
Great burger, dirtiest food place in NYC.
Very delicious burger. You should try it
One of my top 5 burguers (qsr) in the States, a most!
Not fancy, but burgers are very good.
Food is great and cashier was super nice explaining everything.
Delicious burger!
Busy location, quick service. Decent burgers.
My favorite place to enjoy an excellent hamburger and fries
Great burger and fries for the price.
Good place to fastfood, hard to find some times
Best burger near rockfeller Center i have found
I love the cajun fries 48th Street between 6  & Vanderbilt
Quick service and delicious in Midtown. Glad this DC favorite made it to Manhattan.
Good as all five guys and the service was very fast! I can recommend it!
Little slow because they do it right.  Food is always really good.
Busy busy place lol. Great to grab eat and go.
A much bigger space and faster service than other five guys locations
This place's just simple and great at the same time
Pretty fast service and didn't have to wait long.
The service was overall fast and the food was amazing.
great burgers.. fresh & fast
Delicious burgers, a little expensive for the size of the meal offered.
My fav burgers will always be Five Guys..hands down!
Good double cheeseburguer. Big variety of Coke flavours.
Five Guys, five stars! Great burger and chips
Tasty! Lunch hours you hardly can find a sit
GREAT service! Would totally go back next time I'm in the area!
Great food every time I went there
Probably the best fast food restaurant in NYC!
The customers are annoying but the staff is absolutely wonderful here.
The food is good and the establishment is clean.
Great fries. Burgers ok.
good place having meals near Rockfeller center.
All the toppings free and delicious
Simply love their burgers!
Fast and friendly! Hot and fresh food!
Great food.  Following COVID guidelines.
Best fast food burger on the east coast.
Crowded iconic restaurant
The smoothies are so good I needed more
Good food not alot of seating
Best French Fries ever!
Good meal, nice place
Top hamburgers! Fine meat and very tasty!
Good food, just wish service was faster.
Food ok
Gave great amount of fries.
One of the best burgers in the city!
Quick service even though it was super busy!
Fast, lots of topping options, good fries
Best place to get burgers!
They've got fries and burgers all figured out
One of the best hamburger's of NY
Best kind staffs ever!!! Thank you soooo much!
Delucious burgers at a good price
Liked it fries were good
Really really good burgers and fries
Awesome food, fast service.
Always great food and service!
Great burgers fresh fries
Gets very busy during lunch hours...expect delays
Nice place, good services, delicius burgues!!
Just love it
So  nice  food~ enjoy it
Friendly and Helpful staff.
Fast service .. good burgers ..
Great food, quick service
Burgers and hot dogs are lovely
Good burgers and free peanuts
Good burger , free toppings !
Best burgers and fries ever
fast clean. these guys are the best guys
Great food the staff are awesome
Excellent taste !!! I love it !!!
Hospitality and as always great food !

The store was small, so I took take out, but the burgers were average and the fries were delicious. There were several drinks to choose from, but the burgers came out quickly and I was satisfied with my lunch, so I'd give it 5 stars.
Very good burgers. I recommend that if several people (4 or 5) go, do not order more than 2 fries, since they give too many and this way you will save a little money.

Good burger, large, although the meat lacked a little more flavor.
I didn't like the potatoes at all, very salty, somewhat burnt.
You can choose the additional ingredients for free as well as the refill.
Complete snack, French fries in peanut oil, very tasty
The best burger I ate in New York. It was just a shame that there were few seats. One of the employees was excellent, I'm just sorry I don't know the lady's name.

The price-quality ratio of this place is excellent. The burger is very generous and tasty. The fries are the best I've ever had from a fast food chain and maybe even better than a burger joint that doesn't fall into that category. Highly recommended
The interior cleanliness is a bit lacking, but it's delicious. There are unlimited drinks and you can even eat peanuts while you wait. The fries are delicious, but a little salty.
Nice fast food chain in New York. Five Guys offers quality burgers with different toppings to choose from. The fries are really excellent. Great selection of drinks. I highly recommend #burger #nyc
Very good meat. Regular sized sandwich. Prices from $8 and up. Good fries. Be careful when you order, you must specify if you want salad, tomato, onion, mayonnaise etc. inside the sandwich.

Our American host recommended this brand to us for real American burgers, which we loved. The exterior is scary and extremely dirty but the atmosphere is super nice and sublimely good. Not much room to sit.

Nice welcome - wide choice of drinks - welcoming staff - clean toilets - vegetarian and kosher choice - clean tables too - he always adds a little more fries in the bags - I recommend this fast food restaurant and it is among the best burgers in NYC
Great burgers and great fast food... without asking they fill you up with fries. Perhaps the only downside is that they have too little seating
One of the best burgers in New York and the USA. The fries are spectacular and the possibility of free refills makes the drink very cheap. Infinitely superior to Mac Donald's or Burger King!
I love this chain with quality burger and fries

A very good experience and delicious burgers.
They went out of their way to get you there quickly and well. In addition, the potatoes are very abundant and the ingredients that are added are not paid for, so it allows you to eat according to your taste.

It is a delicious burger chain, nothing like the typical ones like McDonald's or Burger King. These look more homemade.
Also, in this particular one they have employees who speak Spanish.
Simple and effective classic recipe. I would have preferred homemade bread rather than industrial bread. The plastic and aluminum packaging is really cheap, I didn't understand the principle..

The woman who took our order was very kind, attentive and gave good advice.
The food was very good ! We had hot dogs and a bacon cheeseburger.

Personally, I think Shake Shack is smoother and more delicious. There was a shake that was only sold here, so I ate it with a hamburger and it really choked me up. Have it with cola. French fries are small, similar to the large size of McDonald's in Korea.

It's a great choice in terms of cost x benefit x flavor. Snacks are assembled in front of you, served in foil. It has shelled peanuts to serve as an appetizer. The fries are unpeeled, and I love them!
Perfect hamburger, delicious fries cooked in peanut oil and generous staff who serve more than the portion!
Great burger, great atmosphere, homemade, delicious and customizable. To test in New York

I love this diner. Very good snack. You pay a price and add as many toppings as you want. But the difference is the fries with the skin in generous quantities and with that famous chorinho. There are only a few units that are very crowded and you can almost never sit down. Look for one further away from Times Square.
I ate at this place more than three times. The service is the best, as is the taste of the burgers. Maximum wait 5 minutes. Try the fries in peanut oil!
Very American place, the best is its refill of very local drinks. Everything is sold separately, burger, fries and drink
The burgers are spectacular, and the fries 10 points. I recommend it! Good attention from the staff
Their potatoes, hamburgers and Panchos are very delicious. If you are in Ny, a must stop. Love.

I recommend Jinshin for a delicious burger with a lot of portions!!!! Even if you order a small size of fried potato, it is no different from other large sizes. The content is completely different from ours!!

McDonald's top-compatible patties are grilled directly in the Meat Kitchen.
It's savory, probably because it's cooked in peanut oil.
The hamburger was the worst I've had since coming here.
Five Guys' burgers are fresh and juicy. You can choose whatever toppings you want and the peanuts are delicious. But the Cajun fries are too salty and spicy.
Good music, natural fries and incredible flavor of the burger
I loved the ordering system for the burgers, where you can create the burger to your liking. Also highlight the cleanliness of the premises.
The service was good, the employee was nice and helpful, and the food was delicious
Excellent hamburger but the restaurants are not very clean.
Excellent "all the way" delicious burger and excellent fries. Well cooked, nothing goes wrong. Thanks for the peanuts and the refill!!!
Good place to eat something quick and at a good price. Very juicy burgers and very good fries.

Classic Five Guys, classic super taste!
The best American fast-food restaurant (in Italy you can find it in Milan and Rome) with few but delicious products!
Very tasty burgers! Restaurant is more for quick visits! As a tourist you should try it!
Good burger and fries. The restaurant is a bit crappy.

To eat on the go!
Super rich and pleasant.
Fast service. Tasty and filling food, with fillings of your choice. I recommend.
A really meaty burger. It's definitely greasier than the Shake Shack burger, but it has its own taste.
The burger is very good. FF forced to try. Abundant quantity of potatoes and excellence
The food is delicious and the place is very distinctive. It's a bit small so go on a weekend or be patient.
Great place to eat a real American burger. The drinks are unlimited. Fast and efficient service
Delicious burgers in a place that does not invite you to think that the food is so good, correct treatment.
Best hamburger in the world, and best fries too

Burger to personalize which is quite nice. The food is very fatty but a cut above the competition when compared to other fast food chains but also a little more expensive... I still recommend it but not every day. Enjoy your food ;)

According to many, they show and experience what fast food is all about in a way. It's more pricey than McDonald's or Burger King, but several times better and tastier. Highly recommended. The McDonald's crap that they serve in the Netherlands, they also serve here. That's too bad. 5 guys is really really better.
Five guys - It brings back memories. The burger was tasty and fresh. Only the cheese slices were a bit out of place. But good. Taste wise my thing :-)
Excellent burger. We even found the fries delicious.
French tourist, this place is good. Pleasant staff who help with understanding the language. Good food.

I thought I had already tried the best burgers, but these from Five Guys are the best! Soft bread, good meat, fresh lettuce and tomato... Too good! From the outside you wouldn't think so but the burgers are delicious and at affordable prices! Highly recommended.

Five Guys is certainly one of the best fast foods I've ever been to. The food is very tasty, fast and the potatoes are sensational. It's a very famous network that almost always follows the "five guys" principle, that is, five people working. The price reflects the quality of the products. I highly recommend it!
It's very good, the fries and the burgers are well seasoned.

Famous snack bar with good prices and tasty burgers. Service is fast. There are tables in the place, although it doesn't appear from the street. The cafeteria is very cold, I went on 2 different days and the air conditioning was freezing. It is worth it! Soda is refillable. Free peanuts.

Great burgers, although on this occasion, the place was not very welcoming. Open bar of Coca Cola with a thousand flavors and aromas, and peanuts. Good vibes waiters, as a brand image. Correct price. A good place to eat quickly.
